text: Android 16 is a upcoming mobile operating system developed and made by Google. The first developer preview version was released on 19 November 2024. The first beta version was released on 23 January 2025. == Development == === Developer preview versions === The first version of Android 16 developer preview was released on 19 November 2024. The second version of developer preview was released on 18 December 2024. === Beta versions and supports === The first version of Android 16 beta was released on 23 January 2025. The second version of Android 16 beta was released on 13 February 2025. The third version of Android 16 beta was released on 13 March 2025. The last version of Android 16 beta was released on 17 April 2025. They can get Android 16 beta from other phone brands such as Oppo, Xiaomi, OnePlus, Vivo, IQOO, Realme and Honor. == References == == Other websites == * Category:Android (operating system)
